QuestData.Title: An End to Beginnings
QuestData.Description:
We're done here. Let's return to Orgrimmar.
When you're ready, hop on one of the wyverns.
It's time to go home.
QuestData.LogDescription: Ride a Horde Wyvern back to Orgrimmar.
QuestData.RewardText:
It's good to be back in Orgrimmar.
I must report to the warchief, but I know what you can do in the meantime...

Objectives.Objective: Horde Wyvern rode back to Orgrimmar
